{"tid":1214431,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日無會議！但聽日都仲可能開會架！","createTime":"2019-06-13T04:21:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T04:49:56.000Z","uid":198233,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0e187e25fe4528a880b8277eeaa2f23ade39049d","tid":1214431,"uid":198233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:21:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3kPUnM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3kPUnM.png&h=3a5642f1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NvRLsHN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNvRLsHN.png&h=f021bd0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄺神亦到左現場解釋<br />\n大家可以留力休息啦<br />\n可以遊走金鐘（靜靜示威be water)<br />\n可以整理物資站<br />\n可以搞你地既策略例如搞港鐵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3CWrWBp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3CWrWBp.png&h=16825f5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聽日要預出黎！因為聽日都有機會開會！<br />\n原本預定星期五都有會開！<br />\n無消息都要記得預早出黎！"},{"pid":"83bb3a463ab729ad44998dee7d76b7a15afca672","tid":1214431,"uid":198233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:22:05.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"9d733f90c880de0a28461169a144ec881096de53","tid":1214431,"uid":198233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:22:58.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"c80b437aa0f9d433cc142c590051185f91c75107","tid":1214431,"uid":198233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:25:43.000Z","msg":"m推"},{"pid":"2e7f4e4efc732a935e07307bb2c67f7b0455e6e9","tid":1214431,"uid":198233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:26:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8141cbd7085f233b88e9a19395bfb745a2be9253","tid":1214431,"uid":198233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:26:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1eca1cdc6ab0d70d9cb45f8c75563f3cf1e2a71d","tid":1214431,"uid":259928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20